        <body>
        <div type="letter">
        <opener><dateline><date when="1917-07-11">July 11, 1917.<dateline></date><salute>Dear <persName key="harriet-monroe">Harriet</persName>:-</salute>
        </opener>
            <p>Here is the review of <persName key="Eunice Tietjen">Eunice Tietjens</persName><title key="profilesFromChina" level="m">’ book</title>. I will send you <persName>Louis Untermeyer</persName><title key="theseTimes" level="m">’s</title> in a day or two. I hope you will like this. <closer>Thanks for your nice letter.
                <p>Affectionately yours,</p></closer>
            </p>
            </div>
